data.description:
*** Back on the Market due to Buyer's financing at no fault to the Seller ***

Meet your new home! This stunning residence boasts a perfect blend of modern elegance and classic charm. Step into a spacious open layout, adorned with beautiful wood floors that seamlessly flow from room to room. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven is designed for both comfort and style. The heart of the home is the inviting living space, where natural light pours in through the windows, highlighting the warmth of the wood floors beneath your feet. Open layout with double French doors beckon you to step outside and discover your private courtyard oasis. Picture sipping your morning coffee or hosting al fresco dinners in this enchanting outdoor space. Situated the  Hillendale II subdivision, this residence offers not just a home, but a lifestyle. Close proximity to Fort Bragg/Liberty, Downtown Fayetteville, Shopping on Skibo!
